%C A161827 The asymptotic density of this sequence is 1 (Cooper and Kennedy, 1989). - _Amiram Eldar_, Jul 10 2020
%H A161827 Curtis N. Cooper and Robert E. Kennedy, <a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/2323194">Chebyshev's inequality and natural density</a>, Amer. Math. Monthly, Vol. 96, No. 2 (1989), pp. 118-124.
%H A161827 Omar E. Pol, <a href="http://www.polprimos.com">Determinacion geometrica de los numeros primos y perfectos</a>
%H A161827 Omar E. Pol, <a href="http://www.polprimos.com/imagenespub/polprdipi.jpg">Divisors and pi(x)</a>
%o A161827 (Python)
%o A161827 from math import isqrt
%o A161827 def A161827(n):
%o A161827     def f(x): return n+isqrt(x)+(isqrt(1+4*x)-1>>1)+isqrt(x+1)-1
%o A161827     m, k = n, f(n)
%o A161827     while m != k: m, k = k, f(k)
%o A161827     return m # _Chai Wah Wu_, Jul 02 2026
